\*\*Revenue Model Card:\*\*  
\- Health Signal Logic: Healthy \= low churn \+ manageable concentration; Pressure \= high churn or concentration creating burden  
\- Headline: Reference retention health, replacement pressure, or concentration dynamics  
\- Example: "High churn generates significant replacement treadmill constraining growth" (Pressure)

\*\*Delivery Architecture Card:\*\*  
